snippet.title: Starfield 1998  //  Bethesda's The 10th Planet Trailer (Unedited)
snippet.description:
Hey #ElderScrollsNation!  Here is the unedited teaser trailer for the cancelled Bethesda 1998 game "The 10th Planet."  This is essentially what Starfield would have been in 1998!

Support my Patreon, Be a Hero, Level Up, Unlock Rewards: ►

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UDGy7hD-fUg

Let me know what you think in the comments below!

Be sure to Like and Share this video so you can help build an awesome Elder Scrolls community so the game never dies and Bethesda knows that Elder Scrolls is loved and followed!  And be sure to Subscribe so you can not only miss the latest news and information, but also so you too can be an important part of the community!

And as always, thank you for watching!
